{"tid":564719,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【名人包場請睇戲】影后貝兒呼籲助黑人小朋友入場睇《黑豹》","createTime":"2018-02-18T09:39:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-18T12:55:39.000Z","uid":41453,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d3c8265b246201dc853d43e89ddfe88aae4c2042","tid":564719,"uid":41453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T09:39:30.000Z","msg":"查特域克保斯曼（Chadwick Boseman）主演新片《黑豹》（Black Panther），屬首部以黑人為主角的超級英雄片，電影周五於北美開畫，首日收7,580萬美元（逾5.9億港元）票房，預計首個周末票房有望突破2億美元（逾15.6億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n當有地有組織發起籌款活動，讓冇能力買票入場嘅黑人小朋友入場睇《黑豹》，奧緹華史賓莎（Octavia Spencer ）同「細威」莎蓮娜威廉絲（Serena Williams）都先後有包場請睇戲。至於奧斯卡影后貝兒娜森（Brie Larson）都已經加入英超行列演Captain Marvel，佢都有喺Twitter留言，呼籲粉絲可以利用其Twitter社交網站平台留言，去幫助冇能力買票人士入場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180218/57846843\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180218%2F57846843&d=VuPL272kMKFTdag9%2BRcrvlzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=56241f50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180218%2F57846843&h=cdb986f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180218/57846843</a>"},{"pid":"924b2ae81a4884c2c72e7f6b60ee97300b6d54ac","tid":564719,"uid":30510,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T09:46:47.000Z","msg":"咩質素嘅人睇咩質素嘅戲"},{"pid":"b5cdc59b7da1f8c69f8ac2c0e74bc82aae688f12","tid":564719,"uid":9586,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T10:18:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要包場畀人入去睇抗日電影嘅感覺一樣"},{"pid":"528c3ac4ffbf75db6ae9a9e57e1651f996aba039","tid":564719,"uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T10:19:35.000Z","msg":"都已經加入英超行列<br />\n心諗做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e4e43213778c09a265d10f